Criar instância compute:

```hcl
resource "oci_core_instance" "web_server" {
  compartment_id      = var.compartment_ocid
  availability_domain = "QnsQ:US-ASHBURN-AD-1"
  display_name        = "web-server-01"
  shape               = "VM.Standard.E4.Flex"

  shape_config {
    ocpus         = 2
    memory_in_gbs = 16
  }

  source_details {
    source_type = "image"
    source_id   = var.image_ocid
  }

  create_vnic_details {
    subnet_id        = oci_core_subnet.public.id
    assign_public_ip = true
  }

  metadata = {
    ssh_authorized_keys = file("~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub")
  }
}
```

**Shapes:** VM.Standard.E4.Flex (AMD), VM.Standard.A1.Flex (ARM, econômico)

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

Instance pool + auto-scaling:

**1. Instance Configuration:**
```hcl
resource "oci_core_instance_configuration" "web_config" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_ocid
  instance_details {
    instance_type = "compute"
    launch_details {
      shape = "VM.Standard.E4.Flex"
      shape_config { ocpus = 2; memory_in_gbs = 16 }
      create_vnic_details { subnet_id = oci_core_subnet.private.id }
    }
  }
}
```

**2. Instance Pool:**
```hcl
resource "oci_core_instance_pool" "web_pool" {
  compartment_id            = var.compartment_ocid
  instance_configuration_id = oci_core_instance_configuration.web_config.id
  size                      = 2
}
```

**3. Auto Scaling:**
```hcl
resource "oci_autoscaling_auto_scaling_configuration" "web" {
  policies {
    capacity { initial = 2; min = 1; max = 10 }
    rules {
      action { type = "CHANGE_COUNT_BY"; value = 1 }
      trigger { metric { metric_type = "CPU_UTILIZATION" }; threshold { operator = "GT"; value = 80 } }
    }
  }
}
```

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

Custom images:

**1. Import de Object Storage:**
```hcl
resource "oci_core_image" "custom" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_ocid
  display_name   = "custom-ubuntu-22-04"
  image_source_details {
    source_type  = "objectStorageUri"
    source_uri   = "oci://bucket/n/namespace/o/image.qcow2"
    launch_mode  = "PARAVIRTUALIZED"
  }
}
```

**2. De boot volume:**
```hcl
resource "oci_core_image" "from_bv" {
  image_source_details {
    source_type    = "bootVolume"
    boot_volume_id = oci_core_boot_volume.golden.id
    launch_mode    = "PARAVIRTUALIZED"
  }
}
```

**3. Use na instância:** source_id = oci_core_image.custom.id

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

Cloud-init via Terraform:

```hcl
resource "oci_core_instance" "app" {
  metadata = {
    user_data = base64encode(<<-EOF
#cloud-config
package_update: true
packages:
  - nginx
  - git
write_files:
  - path: /var/www/html/index.html
    content: |
      <h1>Deployed by Terraform</h1>
runcmd:
  - systemctl enable nginx
  - systemctl start nginx
EOF
    )
  }
}
```

**Com template:**
```hcl
locals {
  cloud_init = templatefile("${path.module}/cloud-init.tftpl", {
    app_port = 8080
  })
}
metadata = { user_data = base64encode(local.cloud_init) }
```

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

Múltiplas instâncias:

**count:**
```hcl
resource "oci_core_instance" "web" {
  count          = 3
  display_name   = "web-server-${count.index + 1}"
  # ...
}
```

**for_each (recomendado):**
```hcl
variable "instances" {
  type = map(object({ shape = string; ocpus = number; ad = string }))
}

resource "oci_core_instance" "servers" {
  for_each = var.instances
  display_name = each.key
  shape        = each.value.shape
  shape_config { ocpus = each.value.ocpus }
}
```

**Diferença:** for_each é mais seguro para mudanças (chave nomeada vs índice)

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

Boot volume customizado:

```hcl
resource "oci_core_instance" "custom_bv" {
  source_details {
    source_type             = "image"
    source_id               = var.image_ocid
    boot_volume_size_in_gbs = 200
  }
}
```

**Backup policy:**
```hcl
resource "oci_core_volume_backup_policy" "daily" {
  schedules {
    period            = "ONE_DAY"
    retention_seconds = 604800
  }
}

resource "oci_core_boot_volume_backup_policy_assignment" "assign" {
  asset_id  = oci_core_instance.custom_bv.boot_volume_id
  policy_id = oci_core_volume_backup_policy.daily.id
}
```

**VPUs:** 10 (balanced), 20 (high), 30 (highest) [MUTABLE]

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs
